* Introduction to &quot;Forbidden Sexual Behavior and Morality: An Objective Re-Examination of Perverse Sex Practices in Different Cultures&quot; (Robert E.L. Masters, 1964) 
* &quot;The Transsexual Phenomenon; a Scientific Report on Transsexualism and Sex Conversion in the Human Male and Female&quot;, (1966) ASIN: B0007HXA76
* Introduction to &quot;Christine Jorgensen; Personal Autobiography&quot; (Christine Jorgenssen, 1967) 
